_:N3b7466d1cd9a450fb7a32d8ddca94090 <http://schema.org/description> "The Treasury Solicitor’s Department (TSol) was a non-ministerial government department that provided legal services to the majority of central government departments and often represented government departments and other publicly funded bodies in England and Wales. On 1 April 2015 TSol became the Government Legal Department (GLD)." .
